o Padrão de rotas do sistema:
 -------------------------------------------
|   ROTA                        |   VERBO   |
 -------------------------------------------
|   /                           |   GET     |
|   /petitions                  |   GET     |
|   /petitions                  |   POST    |
|   /petitions/{id}             |   GET     |
|   /petitions/new              |   POST    |
|   /petitions/{id}/signature   |   POST    |
 -------------------------------------------

